public static class FilteredSet.SignalAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements FilteredSet.ISignal

An abstract adapter class for receiving events from the signal interface. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating receiver objects.

Author:
Erwin Aitenbichler
